{
  "info": {
    "name": "Cobat Risk Engine",
    "description": "Real-time AML transaction risk assessment API.\n\nBase URL: `{{base_url}}/api`\n\nAuth: All `/v1/` routes require `Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}` header.\n\n---\n\n**Assessment status:**\n- `success` — assessment ran without error. Check `allow` for the transaction decision.\n- `pending` — AMLBot wallet screen is asynchronous (up to ~10 min); final decision POSTed to `callbackUrl`.\n- `failed` — internal error; assessment could not be completed.\n\n**Transaction decision (`allow`):**\n- `true` — transaction approved, all rules passed\n- `false` — transaction blocked, one or more rules triggered\n\n**Callback payload** (POSTed to `callbackUrl` on async resolution):\n```json\n{\n  \"assessmentId\": \"risk_...\",\n  \"status\": \"success\",\n  \"allow\": true,\n  \"triggeredRules\": []\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n**Transaction types:**\n- `DEPOSIT` — fiat deposit; no `chain` or `destinationWalletId` needed\n- `BUY_CRYPTO` — requires `chain` + `destinationWalletId`\n- `WITHDRAW_CRYPTO` — requires `chain` + `destinationWalletId`\n\n`counterpartyId` is optional on all types.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "api_key",
      "value": "sk-test-api-key-change-in-production",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
